'''Jingkin waata''', aalso nuo az '''potebl waata''' ar '''paip waata''', a [[waata]] sief anof fi [[jingk]] ah fi [[fuud priparieshan]]. Gluobali, ina 2012, 89% a piipl eh-ab axes tu waata suutebl fi jingk.<ref name=WHO2014>[http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs391/en/ WHO 2014 Water fact sheet] axes 24 May 2015</ref> Nieli 4 bilian eh-ab axes tu paip waata wails aneda 2.3 bilian eh-ab axes tu [[waata wel]] ar poblik tap.<ref name=WHO2014/> 1.8 bilian piipl stil yuuz ansief jingkin waata suos we maita kantaminiet bai [[fiisiz]].<ref name=WHO2014/> Dis kiah rizolt ina [[infekshos dayariya]] laka [[kalara]] ah [[taifaid]] mongx ada diziiz.<ref name=WHO2014/>

